snippet.title: Warparty Launch Trailer - RTS with dinosaurs - out now on PC / Switch / Xbox One / PS4
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/777770/Warparty/
Xbox: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/warparty/9pplfhz2hxdr
Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/warparty-switch
PS4: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/EP8922-CUSA15125_00-WARPARTY00000001

ABOUT:
------------------------------------
Warparty is a real-time strategy game set in the stone-age era. Build your base, recruit and control a group of soldiers, fight and tame fierce dinosaurs and direct the flow of combat. Proper management of resources, skills and map awareness will lead you to victory.
-----------------------------------
www.warpartygame.com
